    </p>

    <footer class="flex flex-col my-4 gap-4 laptop:flex-row">
      <LinkButton
        url="https://drive.google.com/file/d/11hThknDbDiQxv5wgVwM1dPBEbYelLlCr/view?usp=drive_links"
        className="bg-servitec-800 text-white py-4 px-8 rounded-xl font-semibold"
      >
        üí•¬°Reci√©n llegados!
      </LinkButton>
      <LinkButton
        url="#OurServices"
